Task
Is it true that the word begins or ends with the letter "a"?
Create a str variable and assign an arbitrary string value.
Create a result variable and assign it the value of a boolean expression that evaluates to true if the first 
or last letter of the string is a, and false otherwise.

Solution
const str = 'Ava';
const result = str[0] === 'a' || str[str.length -1] === 'a';
